{{Infobox film | name =Doppia coppia con Regina | image =Doppia coppia con Regina.jpg | image_size = | caption = | director =[[Julio Buchs]] | producer = | writer = | narrator = | starring =[[Marisa Mell]] | music =[[Gianni Ferrio]] | cinematography =[[Mario Montuori]] | editor = | distributor = | released = 1972 | runtime = | country = [[Italy]] | language = [[Italian language|Italian]] | budget = }} '''''Doppia coppia con Regina''''' (Spanish title: '''''Alta tensión''''') is a [[Italian films of 1972|1972]] Spanish-Italian film directed by Julio Buchs. It stars [[Marisa Mell]] and [[Gabriele Ferzetti]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mymovies.it/filmografia/?a=73|title=Gabriele Ferzetti |publisher=[[Mymovies.it]]|accessdate=November 30, 2010}}</ref>
